      "english_trans": "So it became as black, barren land."
    },
    "21": {
      "arabic_text": "فَتَنَادَوْا مُصْبِحِينَ",
      "bangla_trans": "ভোরে তারা একে অপরকে ডেকে বললোঃ",
      "word_by_word": {
        "1": {
