          "translate_bn": "তারা বলল"
        },
        "4": {
          "words_ar": "إِنَّا",
          "translate_bn": "নিশ্চয় আমরা"
        },
        "5": {
          "words_ar": "لَضَالُّونَ",
          "translate_bn": "অবশ্যই পথভ্রষ্ট"
        }
      },
      "english_trans": "But when they saw it, they said: Most surely we have gone astray"
    },
    "27": {
      "arabic_text": "بَلْ نَحْنُ مَحْرُومُونَ",
      "bangla_trans": "তাও না- আমার বরং বঞ্চিত হয়েছি।",
      "word_by_word": {
        "1": {
          "words_ar": "بَلْ",
          "translate_bn": "বরং"
        },
        "2": {
          "words_ar": "نَحْنُ",
          "translate_bn": "আমরা"
